(1,'Sand Volcano','🌋','#f5c842','Sand Play · Sensory','Sand Play','10–20 min',ARRAY['Sand','Small plastic bottle','Bicarbonate of soda and vinegar'],ARRAY['Pack sand around a small bottle to make a mountain shape.','Add bicarbonate of soda inside the bottle.','Pour in coloured vinegar and watch the volcano erupt!'],'Baby (0–12 months)','As a baby, they mostly watched while you showed them things. Now they want to take the lead and make things happen for themselves.','Keep face clear of the eruption. Use non-toxic materials.',7,false),
(1,'Ice in Sand','🧊','#f5c842','Sand Play · Sensory','Sand Play','10–20 min',ARRAY['Ice cubes','Sand in a tray'],ARRAY['Bury ice cubes in the sand.','Challenge child to find each cube before it melts.','Feel how the sand around the ice gets cold and wet.'],'Baby (0–12 months)','As a baby, they mostly watched while you showed them things. Now they want to take the lead and make things happen for themselves.','Ensure hands don''t get too cold.',9,false),
(1,'Sand Soup','🥘','#f5c842','Sand Play · Sensory','Sand Play','10–20 min',ARRAY['Sand','Water','Sticks, leaves and pebbles','Old pot and spoon'],ARRAY['Fill an old pot with sand and water.','Add sticks, leaves and pebbles to the soup.','Stir and serve, pretend to taste!'],'Baby (0–12 months)','As a baby, they mostly watched while you showed them things. Now they want to take the lead and make things happen for themselves.','Supervise so sand is not eaten. Wash hands after.',9,false),
