(1,'Buried Ice Gems','💎','#f5c842','Sand Play · Sensory','Sand Play','10–20 min',ARRAY['Ice cubes with glitter frozen inside','Sand in a tray'],ARRAY['Freeze glitter into ice cubes overnight.','Bury the ice gems in the sand.','Dig to find them and watch the glitter appear as they melt.'],'Baby (0–12 months)','As a baby, they mostly watched while you showed them things. Now they want to take the lead and make things happen for themselves.','Ensure hands don''t get too cold.',6,false),
(1,'Sand Alphabet','🔤','#f5c842','Sand Play · Sensory','Sand Play','10–20 min',ARRAY['Wet sand in a tray','Finger or stick for drawing'],ARRAY['Smooth the wet sand flat.','Draw letters in the sand using a finger.','Smooth away and repeat, no paper needed!'],'Baby (0–12 months)','As a baby, they mostly watched while you showed them things. Now they want to take the lead and make things happen for themselves.',NULL,9,false),
(1,'Sieve and Sort','🪄','#f5c842','Sand Play · Sensory','Sand Play','10–20 min',ARRAY['Sand mixed with small shells','Sieve','Two bowls'],ARRAY['Pour sand and shell mixture into a sieve.','Shake the sieve over a bowl to separate the sand from the shells.','Collect the sorted shells in a separate bowl.'],'Baby (0–12 months)','As a baby, they mostly watched while you showed them things. Now they want to take the lead and make things happen for themselves.','Use shells too large to be swallowed.',8,false),

