(2,'Sand Café','☕','#f5c842','Sand Play · Sensory','Sand Play','15–30 min',ARRAY['Sand','Old pots and cups','Paper and crayons for menus'],ARRAY['Draw simple menus on paper together.','Take orders from a toy customer or grown-up.','Make the sand food and serve it on plates.'],'1 year, Wobbler','At one, they explored by grabbing and putting things in their mouth. Now they can use simple tools on purpose, which builds wrist and finger control.',NULL,8,false),
